            "name": "Ruinous Rage",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The rage rider enters a state of pure rage that lasts either for 1 minute, until there are no enemies they can perceive, or until they fall unconscious, whichever comes first. While raging, the rage rider has AC 27 and their spear Strikes deal 2d6+15 damage plus 2d6 persistent bleed damage. While raging, the rage rider can't use actions that have the concentrate trait, except for Seek. After they've stopped raging, a rage rider can't use Rage again for 1 minute.",
